{"tid":1906960,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大器晚成！巴禾32歲之後已收穫15座冠軍獎杯","createTime":"2020-03-02T09:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T16:24:03.000Z","uid":38189,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b2bf8287cc8a76a49aabbe795cdfbc8e229fb6","tid":1906960,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:33:09.000Z","msg":"在今天的聯賽杯決賽中，曼城2-1戰勝維拉成功實現三連冠。 值得一提的是，這是36歲的老門將巴禾職業生涯所收穫的第17座冠軍獎杯，也是年滿32歲之後收穫的第15座冠軍獎杯，堪稱大器晚成。<br />\n<br />\n 巴禾生涯冠軍一覽：<br />\n<br />\n 科洛科洛時期1冠：<br />\n<br />\n 智利甲級聯賽冠軍1座（2006年）<br />\n<br />\n 皇家蘇斯達時期1冠：<br />\n<br />\n 西乙冠軍1座（2009/10賽季）<br />\n<br />\n 巴塞羅那時期8冠：<br />\n<br />\n 西甲冠軍2座（2014/15賽季、2015/16賽季）<br />\n<br />\n 西班牙國王杯冠軍2座（2014/15賽季、2015/16賽季）<br />\n<br />\n 西班牙超級杯冠軍1座（2016）<br />\n<br />\n 歐冠冠軍1座（2014/15賽季）<br />\n<br />\n 歐洲超級杯冠軍1座（2015）<br />\n<br />\n 世俱杯冠軍1座（2015）<br />\n<br />\n 曼城時期5冠：<br />\n<br />\n 英超聯賽冠軍1座（2017/18賽季）<br />\n<br />\n 英格蘭聯賽杯冠軍2座（2017/18賽季、2019/20賽季）<br />\n<br />\n 社區盾杯冠軍2座（2018、2019）<br />\n<br />\n 注：巴禾上賽季長期受傷，僅代表球隊出戰社區盾杯1場，故無緣隨隊奪得上賽季其他3項冠軍<br />\n<br />\n 智利國家隊2冠：<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">美洲杯冠軍2座（2015、2016）</span>"},{"pid":"d5a1d8ca639fdb2e628a0d4f8485821f729867b2","tid":1906960,"uid":1354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98029f8fff65a6bbb52e002226c05c2681917c0c","tid":1906960,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f40d32e0b3d17ab954451b546aca0edc3dfdece","tid":1906960,"uid":131369,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />missi無既野"},{"pid":"aeae8d9f32b2b6da7500cc22a79cb8e4dbd1a01c","tid":1906960,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020